k matter scenarios. For convex models, small structures form more\neasily than in the $\\Lambda$-CDM scenario.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Nov 2016 18:23:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Jan 2020 09:40:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-29"}
