s the experimental\nresult of the muon anomalous magnetic moment. In the resultant mass spectrum,\nsleptons in the first and second generations, bino and winos are all light, and\nthis scenario can be tested at the LHC Run-2 in the near future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Nov 2016 03:14:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Dec 2016 17:30:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 7 Feb 2017 08:40:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-31"}
